let _markdown = "\n\n## Utility Functions\n\nChr3D provides utility functions for common tasks in chromatin conformation analysis.\n\n## Key Functions\n\n### File I/O\n\n* `load_peaks()` - Load peaks from BED format\n* `load_genes()` - Load gene annotations from GTF\n* `load_bedpe()` - Load interactions from BEDPE\n\n### Genome Utilities\n\n* `generate_restriction_map()` - Generate restriction fragment map\n* `get_chromosome_sizes()` - Get chromosome sizes\n* `load_blacklist()` - Load ENCODE blacklist regions\n\n### Annotation\n\n* `annotate_genes()` - Annotate regions with genes\n* `annotate_features()` - Annotate with genomic features\n* `find_overlaps()` - Find overlaps between regions\n\nSee guides for detailed usage examples.\n";
